Example with 
q
:
WMT:NYSE
, and 
window
:
MAX
The window parameter allows selection from a variety of date ranges. Only summary, and graph results are served for searches with window parameter.

GET


https://serpapi.com/search.json?engine=google_finance&q=WMT:NYSE&window=MAX

Code to integrate


Ruby

require "serpapi" 

client = SerpApi::Client.new(
  engine: "google_finance",
  q: "WMT:NYSE",
  window: "MAX",
  api_key: "697c05cd6b6463eba244ca9769758ae5a3d4bc0e6547fc72797084d3d01665d9"
)

results = client.search

